item.dc:creator: @xjadefighter xjadefighter
item.description:
@xjadefighter wrote:

OK first go to your server files and click “run”
Next go to your client or to client.silabsoft.org and log in
you don’t need to put in the ip when your logging in.

Last go through the TuT section on here and see what you can learn about Java.

Good luck.
